title: Hambini Roasts: Trifox X10
content: On the barbecue this week, we have the Trifox X10. This is part one of the review. This frame is available for ~$500-600 from AliExpress and directly from Trifox. Trifox is a Chinese manufacturer and an OEM for a number of the “big boy” brands. This frame is from the same factory with a different […]
